section.def:
*commencement
                (生效日期) means the commencement of this
            Ordinance;

paragraph.content:
a right to require the issue of, or to subscribe for or purchase, or
                    otherwise acquire, any shares in the capital of the company or any subsidiary
                    thereof;

a right to appoint any person, or to be appointed as a
                    director
                    of the company or any subsidiary thereof;
